### **Playing State Layout**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  DrawMaster                                               👤 User2516  120 điểm              │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ NGƯỜI CHƠI          │  Từ: _ _ _ _  ⏰ 45s  🎯 Round: 2/3  💯 Điểm: 120                      │
├─────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────┤
│😊 User2516 (Vẽ)     │                                                 │    TRÒ CHUYỆN        │
│   120 điểm          │               DRAWING CANVAS                    │ ┌─────────────────────┐│
│👤 Player2           │                 600x400px                       │ │User1: con mèo?      ││
│   0 điểm            │                                                 │ │User2: chó!          ││
│👤 Player3           │                                                 │ │🎨 Từ cần vẽ: MÈO   ││
│   45 điểm           │                                                 │ │User3: mèo!          ││
│👤 Player4           │                                                 │ │🎉 User3 đã đoán đúng││
│   30 điểm           │                                                 │ └─────────────────────┘│
├─────────────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────────┤ [Input] [Gửi]        │
│                     │ Tools: ✏️[Bút] 🧽[Tẩy] 🎨[Colors] 📏[Size] 🗑️[Xóa] │                       │
└─────────────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────────┴───────────────────────┘
```

## 🔧 **TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION**

### **Modern Game Architecture**
```csharp
✅ State Management: Waiting → Playing → End
✅ Drawing System: Bitmap + Graphics với GDI+
✅ Timer Management: System.Windows.Forms.Timer
✅ Event-Driven: Mouse events cho drawing
✅ Dynamic UI: Runtime control creation
✅ Smooth Animation: Character và UI effects
```

### **Drawing Engine Features**
- **Canvas Resolution**: 600x400px optimized
- **Pen Technology**: LineCap.Round cho smooth drawing
- **Color System**: RGB color palette selection
- **Brush Dynamics**: Variable size với TrackBar
- **Eraser Logic**: White color painting technique
- **Real-time Rendering**: Immediate visual feedback

### **Game Logic Implementation**
- **Word Bank**: Vietnamese words collection
- **Random Selection**: Secure random word picking
- **Score Calculation**: Time-based scoring algorithm
- **Round Progression**: Automatic game flow
- **Chat Integration**: Message parsing và guess detection

## 🎮 **GAMEPLAY FEATURES**

### **Enhanced User Experience**
- ✅ **Intuitive Controls**: Easy-to-use drawing tools
- ✅ **Visual Feedback**: Immediate response to user actions
- ✅ **Game Progression**: Clear round và score indicators
- ✅ **Social Interaction**: Real-time chat integration
- ✅ **Vietnamese Localization**: 100% tiếng Việt

### **Creative Drawing Tools**
- **Multi-Color Palette**: 6 essential colors
- **Variable Brush Size**: 1-10px range
- **Smart Eraser**: Context-aware erasing
- **Canvas Management**: Clear và reset functionality
- **Professional Feel**: Industry-standard drawing experience

