## 🎨 **VISUAL DESIGN ELEMENTS**

### **Color Palette**
- **Primary Blue**: #2D7DF5 (Gradient background)
- **Secondary Blue**: #1E5AC8 (Headers)
- **Orange Accent**: #FFA500 (Action buttons)
- **Yellow Avatar**: #FFC107 (User avatars)
- **White Clean**: #FFFFFF (Canvas và panels)
- **Light Blue**: #F8FAFF (Tool backgrounds)

### **Typography System**
- **Game Title**: Segoe UI 28pt Bold
- **Headers**: Segoe UI 16-18pt Bold
- **UI Text**: Segoe UI 10-12pt Regular
- **Score/Timer**: Segoe UI 16pt Bold
- **Chat**: Segoe UI 9pt Regular

### **Icon System**
- **Drawing Tools**: ✏️🧽🎨📏🗑️
