## 🎯 **GAME FLOW DIAGRAM**

```
🔐 Login → 🏠 Waiting Room → ✅ Ready Check → 🎮 Game Start
                ↓
🎨 Drawing Phase → 💬 Guessing → 🏆 Scoring → 🔄 Next Round
                ↓
📊 Final Score → 🎉 Results → 🔄 Play Again
```

